<para id="fs-id1164564724643">Consider these indices of refraction: glass: 1.52, air: 1.0003, water: 1.333. Put these materials in order from the one in which the speed of light is fastest to the one in which it is slowest.</para>
<list id="fs-id1164566525307" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
<item>The speed of light in water > the speed of light in air > the speed of light in glass.</item>
<item>The speed of light in glass > the speed of light in water > the speed of light in air.</item>
<item>The speed of light in air > the speed of light in water > the speed of light in glass.</item>
<item>The speed of light in glass > the speed of light in air > the speed of light in water.</item>
</list>
</problem>
</exercise>
